ay Animals Day</h3></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:5;--c-lg:5"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-31_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dYtuZ bTisNR pf-32_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAWBJg ciQrUe pf-33_ animate-float-shadow">節日的產生與用意</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAWBJg ciQrUe pf-35_ animate-float-shadow">關愛流浪動物的重要性</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAWBJg ciQrUe pf-37_ animate-float-shadow">如何關愛流浪動物</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAWBJg ciQrUe pf-39_ animate-float-shadow">杜絕流浪動物產生的方法</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-5cde" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-eSxRXt eFcmyr pf-45_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jNHqnW kAyuLL"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-46_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-47_ pf-bg-lazy"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-48_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-49_">節日的產生與用意</h3><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cTAIfT imxxrC pf-53_"><i class="sc-faUpoM cTsgqM pf-54_ pfa pfa-quote-left" data-pf-type="Icon"></i><p class="sc-ehCJOs iphVAH pf-55_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">8/20國際流浪動物日起源於美國的「國際流浪動物日基金會」（International Homeless Animals' Day Foundation）。這個組織深知，全球范圍內許多流浪動物面臨著困境，迫切需要我們的關懷和協助。流浪動物所經歷的苦難，從飢餓、疾病，到虐待和孤獨，強烈呼籲我們對它們承擔起責任。因此，8/20國際流浪動物日的主旨在於引起社會關注，提升人們對動物權益的認識。這個節日展現了我們對這些毫無防備的生命的關懷，同時激勵大眾積極參與。</p><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-57_">&nbsp;</h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-6ad4" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-eSxRXt eFcmyr pf-330_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jNHqnW kAyuLL"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-329_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-319_ pf-bg-lazy"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-328_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-321_">關愛流浪動物的重要性</h3><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cTAIfT imxxrC pf-327_"><i class="sc-faUpoM cTsgqM pf-322_ pfa pfa-quote-left" data-pf-type="Icon"></i><p class="sc-ehCJOs iphVAH pf-324_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">流浪動物的處境觸動人心。它們無依無靠，在危險和不確定中挣扎求生。飢餓、疾病和虐待將它們的生活籠罩，然而我們不能視而不見。流浪動物同樣有情感，同樣渴望被愛，被關心。我們的關懷為它們帶來一絲希望，助力它們度過艱難。我們應深刻明白，流浪動物不僅僅是客觀存在，它們擁有生命，值得我們的尊重和呵護。</p><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-326_">&nbsp;</h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-3a2f" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-eSxRXt eFcmyr pf-342_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jNHqnW kAyuLL"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-341_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-331_ pf-bg-lazy"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-340_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-333_">如何關愛流浪動物</h3><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cTAIfT imxxrC pf-339_"><i class="sc-faUpoM cTsgqM pf-334_ pfa pfa-quote-left" data-pf-type="Icon"></i><p class="sc-ehCJOs iphVAH pf-336_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">愛心與關懷能夠改變流浪動物的命運，我們每個人都有責任參與其中。首先，我們可以選擇領養而非購買寵物，這樣有助於減少流浪動物的數量，並將它們帶進我們溫馨的家庭。同時，支持流浪動物庇護所，為它們提供食物、水和醫療照顧，確保它們基本需求的得到滿足。作為寵物主人，我們更應負起愛護、訓練和醫療照護的責任，確保寵物的幸福和健康。</p><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-338_">&nbsp;</h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-be86" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-eSxRXt eFcmyr pf-354_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jNHqnW kAyuLL"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-353_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-343_ pf-bg-lazy"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-352_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-345_">杜絕流浪動物產生的方法</h3><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-cTAIfT imxxrC pf-351_"><i class="sc-faUpoM cTsgqM pf-346_ pfa pfa-quote-left" data-pf-type="Icon"></i><p class="sc-ehCJOs iphVAH pf-348_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">解決流浪動物問題需要綜合的措施。鼓勵寵物主人進行負責任的寵物節育，是解決源頭問題的關鍵。同時，透過教育和宣傳，我們可以提高公眾對動物權益和寵物責任的認識，降低棄養和忽視等問題的發生率。</p><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-350_">&nbsp;</h3></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-f103" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-eSxRXt eFcmyr pf-236_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-jNHqnW kAyuLL"><div class="sc-efQSVx kdrjec pf-237_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fvpsdx eVTiRY pf-238_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-239_">台灣社會關注的流浪動物議題</h3><div class="sc-eaPPdL hLORHL pf-241_ pf-r pf-r-ew pf-c-ct pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--ew-xs:1;--ew-md:3" data-pf-type="ContentList"><div class="pf-c"><div data-pf-type="ContentListItem" class="sc-hzuobC kf